Argentina.title: M3 for Argentina
Argentina.notes:
M3 comprises M2, fixed deposits, and other deposits in national and foreign currency of state and local governments, public nonfinancial corporations, private sector, and residents abroad with banking institutions.

Brazil.title: M3 for Brazil
Brazil.notes:
M3 comprises M2 plus shares in financial investment funds and the net position of the securities used in the repurchase agreements transactions with money holding sectors.

Saudi Arabia.title: M3 for Saudi Arabia
Saudi Arabia.notes:
M3 comprises M2 and other quasi-monetary liabilities of commercial banks. Other quasi-monetary liabilities comprise foreign currency deposits of businesses, individuals, and government entities; marginal deposits for letters of credit, outstanding remittances; and banks' repurchase agreements with the private sector.
